## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of recent data and the inherent biases present in some sources. The complexity of political polarization means that not all contributing factors can be fully explored in this report. Additionally, the dynamic nature of political landscapes means that findings may evolve over time as new data and insights emerge.